<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1107000' id='t-1107000'>But over the years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1110000' id='t-1110000'>10 years later, the snow packs eroded,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1112000' id='t-1112000'>and, if you notice, the trees have started turning yellow.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1114000' id='t-1114000'>The water level of the lake has started drying up.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1119000' id='t-1119000'>A few years later, there's no snow left at all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1122000' id='t-1122000'>And all the trees have turned brown.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1126000' id='t-1126000'>This year, unfortunately the lakebed's</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1128000' id='t-1128000'>turned into an absolute cracked dry bed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1131000' id='t-1131000'>And I fear, if we do nothing for our planet,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1134000' id='t-1134000'>in 20 years, it's going to look like this.</span>
